
# CodSoft Internship - Java Development

## Intern Details
- Name: P. Janani
- Internship Domain: Java Development
- Organization: CodSoft

## Task Title
Student Grade Calculator

## Task Description
This task is a console-based Java application that calculates the total marks, average percentage, and grade of a student based on the marks entered for different subjects.

The user inputs marks for multiple subjects, and the program computes:
- Total Marks
- Average Percentage
- Grade based on percentage

The application demonstrates the use of basic Java concepts and logical implementation.

## Features
- Accepts marks input for multiple subjects
- Calculates total marks
- Computes average percentage
- Assigns grade based on performance
- Displays final result clearly

## Technologies Used
- Java
- JDK (Java Development Kit)
- Console Interface

## Concepts Used
- Variables and Data Types
- Arithmetic Operations
- Conditional Statements (if-else)
- Loops
- Scanner Class



## Author
P. Janani
